Hi 

first you need to place the two hidden folders into your home directory
their names are .conky and .scripts (Ctrl + H to see them xD ) 

second place the fonts from the font folder into yours at /home/.fonts 
and in a terminal type 'sudo fc-cache -f -v' for updating the font cache

third this is the comand you need if yo follow this instructions XD

conky -c ~/.conky/conkyrc3 &

enjoy

messages to my email
cruznickbjm@gmail.com 


